# Structured-log JSON customizers are loaded by StructuredLogFormatterFactory
# via SpringFactoriesLoader during Logback initialization, which happens BEFORE
# the Spring application context exists. Registering via @Component would be
# too late - the customizer must be wired through this SPI file.
org.springframework.boot.logging.structured.StructuredLoggingJsonMembersCustomizer=com.prodready.social.observability.EcsTraceFieldsCustomizer
